mb|P?|nt|^b@2^z@3^^|lb|*bBid for South.^^1d|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|These days the distributions where some open 1NT are more flexible. Some would open 1NT with my hand. But I still believe that you should only open 1NT when your hand contains at most 1 doubleton e.g. 5-3-3-2 4-4-3-2 or 4-3-3-3 distribution.|
