nt|^b@2^z@3^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Otherwise you start to lose the precision of opening 1NT. And on this hand if partner is 5-5 in the majors we will end up in a 5-2 fit. Because partner with 5-5 in the majors will give me a choice of hearts or spades, assuming I have 3 card support at least in one of them.|
