nt|^b@2^z@3^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Partner assumes you have at least a doubleton in every suit. So you could easily end up in a 6-1 or even a 5-1 fit. Just because it is legal doesn't mean you should do it.|
