nt|^b@2^z@3^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|However, over 1 of a minor it is okay to double with a doubleton in the unbid minor because partner will strain to bid a major. So I would have doubled with the West hand although pass is fine.|
